<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About the Co-Founder | CodeElevate</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      margin: 50px auto;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .content {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .image {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .image img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
        border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .text {
      flex: 2;
    }

    .text h2 {
      color: #1f3c88;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .text p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .highlights {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .highlights h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #0056b3;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .highlights ul {
      list-style: square;
      margin-left: 20px;
      color: #444;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      background-color: #f1f5f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 5px solid #1f3c88;
      margin-top: 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    } 
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      .header p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .content {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .text h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .text p {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .highlights h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .image img {
        max-width: 220px;
      }

      .highlight-box {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>About the Co-Founder</h1>
      <p>Meet the visionary mind behind CodeElevate — shaping careers, building futures.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="image">
        <img src="/images/ph1.jpeg" alt="Co-Founder Photo" class="std-img" >
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <h2>Lokesh Kumar</h2>
        <p>
          Lokesh Kumar, co-founder of <strong>CodeElevate</strong>, is a passionate software developer and educator
        </p>
        <p>
          A full-stack expert in both MERN stack and Java backend technologies, he brings real-world experience from working on enterprise-grade projects and global tech collaborations.
        </p>
        <p>
          He has built this platform to empower students from Tier 2 and Tier 3 cities to compete globally and get placed in top companies like <strong>Google, Amazon, Microsoft, and Meta</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlights">
      <h3>Why Learn from Lokesh Kumar?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-world curriculum with live projects</li>
        <li>Personal mentorship and career guidance</li>
        <li>Industry-level interview preparation</li>
        <li>Weekly coding contests & mock interviews</li>
        <li>100+ students placed in FAANG & unicorn startups</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Mission:</strong> “To make high-quality technical education accessible and career-oriented for every ambitious learner, regardless of background.”
        <br><br>
        <strong>Vision:</strong> “To be the most trusted launchpad for software careers in India.”
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
